 <text id="F3025T">
  <front id="d2">
   <div1 type="summary" id="d3">
    <p>Demus talks about the difficulties he has encountered in getting paid and the resulting
     conflict with his wife.</p>
   </div1>
  </front>

  <body id="d4">
   <div1 type="letter" id="d5">
    <head>
     <name type="recipient">Mary Jane Demus</name>
    </head>

    <opener>
     <dateline>
      <date value="1865-02-08"><orig reg="February">Febury</orig> the 8th 1865</date>
      <name type="place">Morris <orig reg="island">iland</orig></name>
     </dateline>
     <salute/>
    </opener>

    <p>I <orig reg="Receive">Receve</orig>
     <orig reg="your">yor</orig> kind letter this <orig reg="Morning">Mornen</orig> and it <orig
      reg="found">fond</orig> Me Well But I hope <orig reg="When">Whean</orig>
     <orig reg="these">thes</orig>
     <orig reg="few">fu</orig> lines Reach you <orig reg="they">tha</orig>
     <orig reg="May">Ma</orig> find Well But i am <orig reg="very">verry</orig> sorry that i <orig
      reg="have">heave</orig>
     <orig reg="Disturb">Desturb</orig>
     <orig reg="your">yor</orig> Mind so Much just on <orig reg="account">a Cont</orig> of Me try to
      <orig reg="Make">Mak</orig>
     <orig reg="Myself">Mi Celf</orig> Big But as you <orig reg="Wrote">Rot</orig> in the last
     letter <orig reg="Why">Wiy</orig> I <orig reg="hope">hoppe</orig> that you Will forgive Me for
     What i <orig reg="have">heave</orig>
     <orig reg="Done">Dun</orig> and Now i Will tell you the <orig reg="Reason">Reasen</orig> that i
      <orig reg="done">dun</orig> it <orig reg="Was">Wos</orig>
     <orig reg="because">becos</orig> i <orig reg="thought">thot</orig> that We <orig reg="Would"
      >Wod</orig> be <orig reg="paid">pad</orig> of in a <orig reg="short">sort</orig>
     <orig reg="time">tim</orig> and then i <orig reg="Would">Wod</orig>
     <orig reg="just">jest</orig> give him a hundred <orig reg="dollars">dollers</orig> in place of
     it But as it <orig reg="happened">hapen</orig> the <orig reg="Regiment">Redgment</orig> got
      <unclear>Carded</unclear>
     <unclear>Wi</unclear> We did Not get <orig reg="paid">pad</orig> of But i hope you Will <orig
      reg="Make">Mak</orig>
     <orig reg="yourself">yor Celf</orig> easy <orig reg="about">a Bout</orig> it <orig reg="for"
      >fer</orig> i <orig reg="have">heave</orig>
     <orig reg="Wrote">Rote</orig> to <orig reg="Jacob">Jacop</orig>
     <orig reg="about">a Bout</orig> it and i <orig reg="Just">Jest</orig> took him all <orig
      reg="about">a Bout</orig> it and i think that it Will Be all <orig reg="Right">Rite</orig> as
      <orig reg="soon">son</orig> as i get <orig reg="answer">anser</orig>
     <orig reg="from">frum</orig> him <orig reg="for">fer</orig> he <orig reg="Knows">Nows</orig>
     that he Will Not lost <orig reg="any">eny</orig> by it so you Can make <orig reg="yourself">yor
      Celf</orig> easy till I <orig reg="Write">Rite</orig>
     <orig reg="again">a gane</orig></p>

    <p>But i <orig reg="Would">Wod</orig> be very sorry if it <orig reg="Would">Wod</orig>
     <orig reg="Cause">Cos</orig>
     <orig reg="you">u</orig> and I to part But if it is <orig reg="your">yor</orig> Will <orig
      reg="Why">Wiy</orig> i <orig reg="Can't">Cant</orig>
     <orig reg="help">healp</orig> it <orig reg="for">fer</orig>
     <orig reg="your">yor</orig> Will is your <orig reg="pleasure">pleser</orig></p>

    <p>But still i shall <orig reg="Write">Rite</orig> and tell you all <orig reg="about">a
     Boat</orig> it as <orig reg="soon">son</orig> as i get a letter <orig reg="from">frum</orig>
     <orig reg="Jacob">Jacop</orig> E. Christy</p>

    <p>And then i Will <orig reg="Write">Rite</orig>
     <orig reg="again">a gane</orig><lb/>
     <orig reg="No">Now</orig>
     <orig reg="More">Mor</orig> at present</p>

    <closer>
     <salute/>
     <signed>David Demus to Mrs <orig reg="Mary">Marry</orig> Jane Demus</signed>
     <seg type="postscript"><orig reg="please">pleas</orig> Direct <orig reg="your">yor</orig>
      letter to <orig reg="Morris">Moris</orig>
      <orig reg="island">iland</orig> South <orig reg="Carolina">Carlina</orig><lb/><lb/> Co. R.
      54th Mass. <orig reg="volunteer">volentear</orig><lb/> in the <orig reg="Post">Poast</orig>
      <orig reg="Commissary">Comemessary</orig></seg>
    </closer>
   </div1>
  </body>
 </text>
